  "title": "Full Stack Developer (Survey Creation) - 1 Year @ Central",
  "description": "<p><strong>We are seeking a Full Stack Developer with extensive experience in building high-performing front-end applications using React JS and Redux Toolkit for state management, as well as robust backend applications with </strong><u><strong>Node JS and Python</strong></u><strong>. The ideal candidate will have a keen eye for detail, a commitment to best practices, a security-first mindset, and strong communication and collaboration skills. Experience in both frontend and backend development is a plus.</strong></p><p><u><strong>Job Description:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Develop and maintain high-quality front-end applications using <u>React JS; utilise Redux Toolkit</u> for efficient state management</li><li>Design and implement high-performing backend applications using <u>Node JS, Python, Streamlit</u>; </li><li>Ensure the security and performance of backend applications</li><li>Should have knowledge to integrate <u>AWS Cloud services</u></li><li>Conduct thorough code reviews and provide constructive feedback</li><li>Follow best practices for coding, testing, and deployment; Work closely with design and product teams to ensure a seamless user experience.</li></ul><p><u><strong>Job Requirement:</strong></u></p><ul><li>Experience in both frontend and backend development</li><li>Experience with <u>ReactJS, Python, Redux, Streamlit</u></li><li>Experience in creation/maintenance of <u>APIs using Node.js</u></li><li>Good knowledge of backend technologies and <u>AWS Cloud services</u></li><li>Strong attention to detail and commitment to producing high-quality work</li><li>Ability to conduct thorough and constructive pull request reviews</li></ul>",
